  stimulus_text = 'The city council approved a plan to install a new public park in the neighborhood, a move that will provide the community with a much needed space for recreation and relaxation. Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
