  stimulus_text = 'The author of the passage suggests that the invention of optical tweezers is a major breakthrough in medical and scientific research. The text provides an example of this breakthrough: a new way to manipulate particles for study. This is an example of what the text claims is a major breakthrough. Researchers note that the pattern described above remained consistent across repeated observations, suggesting the finding was not a one-time anomaly. They caution that local conditions can still vary, yet the overall relationship held in each documented case.',
