  stimulus_text = 'A group of students was asked to write a short story about a time they had to overcome a challenge. One student wrote the following:  "I was nervous as I waited for my turn, but I knew I could do it. I took a deep breath and went into the audition room.  When I finished, the judges told me I did great!  And I was proud of myself."  Which choice most effectively combines the sentences in this excerpt to produce a more sophisticated and mature writing style?',
